user.bio: Amateur beer taster looking to go pro.
Seen big hitters come and go and crash and burn on here. Untapped is not a fad. It's for life. No toast whores please.
Been trying different beers for many years. Porters, Stouts, and ESB are my favorites. Also love Cascadian Dark Ales
Let's set up a trade. I like beer I can't get in my area.

Heavy metal activist, arsenal/adelaide crows fan and craft beer snob.
Instagram - beernoevil, 
Twitter - beernoeviloz
